description:
Unsurpassed imaging excellence
with a 200MP AI camera 200MP imaging system
Clear details and stunning night shots
Equipped with a flagship-level 200MP main camera, powerful hardware and OIS (optical image stabilisation), the Redmi Note 14 Pro+ 5G provides clearer details and purer night shots.
Xiaomi Imaging Engine AI-boosted algorithm 4X lossless zoom
Optical-level lossless zoom With both 2X and 4X optical-grade lossless zoom, you can easily switch between different focal lengths to frame your shot without a pixel out of place
Extraordinary night shots Let your iconic moments shine
RAW algorithms have been further refined to retain more image details and make night shots even more stunning.
High-dynamic
Clarity in light and shadow
With Smart-ISO Pro, Redmi Note 14 Pro+ 5G delivers incredible HDR photos by automatically adjusting the phone camera to capture better details in both dark and bright areas of a scene. It ensures each photo is not overexposed and makes dark areas clearer, leading to a better light and shadow balance.
Powerful AI tools Transform your photos into masterpieces
Natural-looking portraits Show off your inner charm
Take stunning and artistic half-body portraits without the need for editing with a beautifully blurred background that draws the eye to your subject. Capture more excitement
Thanks to powerful hardware and in-depth tuning of algorithms, capturing beautiful moments has never been easier.
Motion Tracking Capture mode provides you with low-latency, high-quality and high-dynamic photo capture. Snap candid and spontaneous moments with pets and kids, or exhilarating highlights at concerts and sports games with better clarity Dynamic shots Capture and record more of life's beauty and magical moments
Now you can take dynamic shots and select your favorite ones from them; with three export options: photo, video, and GIF to preserve the memories for you.
